To launch learning you need to 00 folder with pretrained potential. Al other folders provided

Adjust to system (not a hard deal, small twicks needed):
job.sl
lammps_setup
vasp/sample_in

To run (buy default job is run on 2 nodes for 12 hours):
sbatch job.sl

Check the last iteration done;
Restart with last iteration if broke down in the middle (the simplest way);
To do so 
rm -rf LAST_ITER
update job.sl to start with LAST_ITER

Convergence is reached when no new configurations are selected.
